so im sure cort will post about this too..but..

i set him up on vh1's motormouth..where you get the person to sing in the car while hidden cameras tape what he is doing..

it was pretty funny. they told me i should "provoke" him..i didnt even have too!

it was great.

dont know if it will be on tv..maybe..he was acting crazy so there is a good chance that we might..but

the "revealing" time..they were like "hey cort do you want to be on tv?" and hes like "what?"

and they go "cuz youre on vh1's motormouth!!!!" and rush the car... cort just sits there and is all "what are you talking about" to the dude...the most subtle reaction ever!

hahaha.

i made chicken/vege dumplings..spanich rice..and sauted mushrooms.. and im not stoned..

i had golden grahams for breakfast...yep thats right..i said it.
now i can finally say, "yeah ive never been to graceland, but ive been to graceland too."

uhn uh..man.
my knuckles might be broken.. my ear lobe is definatly ripped.. my ribs are bruised.. my hands are cut.. and my toe wont stop bleeding..

i knew what was goign to happen.. what do you expect with an empty stomach.. a head full of medication.. and a bunch of 151 in your blood..

cort took a 6 foot dive off a fence onto concrete.. and i jump the fence too.. to help him? no. instead i found a shopping cart, picked it up and threw it on top of him.. then started kicking him..

i also jumped on the hood of friends car and put a huge dent in it. i felt really bad. still do. i havent felt this bad since i tattooed a friends forehead with a knife and a sharpie while he was passed out.

cort and i fought somewhere else too..in the street in front of pats house i think.at 6am.. we lost his key so we had to break in.. somebody saw us, called the cops, and they eventually came. but,we were passed out. 

cort awoke to the cops outside his window throwing rocks at him to wake up. he didnt know it was them so he yells "leave me the fuck alone or ill fuck you in the ass!", thinking that it was one of us. the cop turned to his buddies and says, "hey, this guy just told me he was going to fuck me in the ass"

oh cort, you crazy bastard.

for fun

another? the pancake is dee-lish!
my neck itches..bigtime..i said my neck itches..yes thats what i said..twice,even..oh snap? yeah thats what i said back in 8th grade..everything to do with it. i said hola..big fucking deal..dadaadadarearare.. oh god no..oh god yes! i forget what movie thats from, but my throat hurts..whats what? are you? not you? then who? .....who stole the cookies from the cookie jar. who me? yes you? couldnt be? then who? A B C? ZINC, perhaps? mmmmm mmmmmmm good. whose got xanax? i keep coughing...fuck.

S-Y-R-U-P!!! tard...of me?

backing out? approaching? your life is what? out with it! i just said that. i did. of course not, but who cares who knows. its my new my beer..creep pancake beer. this keyboard is stick. now your just talking circles. you know? hey!

fast food. i ate bic mac...secret sauce. what'd you get? oh a limelade..why didnt you get uhh..what do you call it? what did you get? just a limeade right..just a limeade right..a cherry limeade ok...i was aobut to say.. THATS THE POINT!!!

you think when somebody says "hey, id like you to meet my friend" you automatically assume that they are friends, right?

well last night was not the case. Ryan Too brought some dude over to morgan and maggies house that he found on the street.

i thought they were friends so i did the usual shit talking to him, not knowing that THEY DIDNT FUCKING KNOW EACH OTHER!!

anyway, after much drinking and what not we end up having to drive him home..and this is where i figured out that they had only known each other for about 2 hours we drop him off at home..i guess it was his home..it was more like a corner in orange mound at 3.30am

the guy was a complete DOUCHE BAG!!!

"man these white boys are fucking dumb...im all hard..blah blah blah" fuck you dude..you were in no way HARD, COOL, TOUGH...you were and are a DOUCHE BAG.. end of story.
